{"tid":1348754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班仆街咪再話香港政府冇能力管治我地！","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:09:08.000Z","uid":60284,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e474b2ffb77d010c21b114515219b12cbfdd81b","tid":1348754,"uid":60284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:52:42.000Z","msg":"陶傑喺早一排衝立法會嘅時候，曾經有講過關於<span style=\"color: red;\"> 政府無力管治</span> 嘅後果，當中亦提及過基本法係有明文顯示中央可以單方面宣布香港進入<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>緊急狀態</strong></span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ipB3PHoQx-o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FipB3PHoQx-o&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=ed89771f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ipB3PHoQx-o</a><br />\n8:51-10:10 <br />\n<br />\n咁緊急狀態之後又點呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc9.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fimages%2Fbasiclawtext_doc9.pdf&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=24390529\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/tc/basiclawtext/images/basiclawtext_doc9.pdf</a><br />\n第5頁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbpR92h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbpR92h.png&h=135ec35a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本法上面寫，全國人大常委會決定宣布戰爭狀態，或因特別行政區發生其政府不能控制的危及國家統一，或安全的動亂，而決定特別行政區進入緊急狀態，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中央人民政府可頒布命令，將有關全國性法律在香港實施</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n即係中都唔撚使你送，一國兩制直接玩撚完。<br />\n<br />\n再睇返元朗哩件事，個心係咪有少少寒寒地？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港政府今次到底謀算緊啲乜嘢</span>？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/brfh5AR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbrfh5AR.png&h=e2702a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然有人覺得佢哋又係衰戇鳩，但為咗保障自己冇得唔諗深一層。<br />\n<br />\n揾黑社會出嚟打市民，報警又唔撚理，警署落埋閘，議員面皮好撚厚咁出嚟開記招。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇返歷史，共匪不嬲最鍾意充當着 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「拯救人民」</strong></span> 嘅角色，美其名地實行佢嘅統治，當香港真係好似陶傑引用基本法所講嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「無力管治」</strong></span>，發生咩事都好政府只做一個<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旁觀</span></span></strong>嘅角色，市民叫天不應叫地不聞。但更可悲嘅係呢一幕已經上映左</span>。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所謂無力管治嘅界線到底係邊</span></strong>？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中央會唔會出手？又或者呢一個會唔會就係林鄭嘅政治任務</span></span>？<br />\n<br />\n當然中國真係要咁做，涉及好多關於國際形勢嘅問題，但如果真係呢？諗到呢啲就覺得好無力，歡迎理性討論策略。<br />\n<br />\n第一次寫post唔識排版請見諒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8066a82bc6082f027b564bd7623bb94335f9003","tid":1348754,"uid":60284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:10:11.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid":"0dc7f1a8504d05b8592ad0f3c8e63fd8c6073e34","tid":1348754,"uid":136027,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"支持中共全面接管<br />\n肅清全港外資以及外國勢力<br />\n利申 焦土"},{"pid":"d6f27a91f9b7e1a0290fe352c3c961fe0472b4fc","tid":1348754,"uid":81273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"快撚d<br />\n有機會博到美軍進場<br />\n衰極都係變深圳上海北京 <br />\n工照返"},{"pid":"3add4c63202e4e365a06a179fba3a116362e6e0f","tid":1348754,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:17:41.000Z","msg":"圍村地圖APP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推上熱門 share 比出嚟元朗嘅人睇"},{"pid":"073d88f364529f9b70d8866b8c2f75e07762ac95","tid":1348754,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"圍村地圖APP<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354665</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\